data.description: Welcome Home! Experience luxury living in this stunning 2 story, 3200 sq ft masterpiece! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and a spacious 2 car garage, this home has it all! Indulge in a newly rejuvenated kitchen, perfect for culinary adventures. Relax and entertain in style on the patio and take a dip in your very own sparkling pool. Need a space to focus or break a sweat? This home boasts an office/study and a workout room. And don't forget about the cedar closet for all your storage needs. Move-in ready and waiting for you to call it home. Act fast to get in before summer and enjoy the ultimate oasis in your backyard!
